cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.IR 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision (CV) and machine learning (LG) techniques for face recognition and facial attribute prediction. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category is cs.CV. Additionally, the paper proposes a novel deep learning architecture for this task, which falls under the sub-category of artificial intelligence (AI). The paper also uses multiple datasets for evaluation, which could fall under the sub-categories of multimedia (MM) and information retrieval (IR).
